window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jacob and his friends might have made it out of Hell, but now they face something even more daunting: Heaven.</p> <p>Someone has been killing in Jacob’s name, and the Exalted One and his minions are not happy.</p> <p>Now, Jake’s on trial, and he’s got to figure out how to clear his name.</p> <p>In order to do that, he must gain allies, battle evil cultists, and take on Demon King Beelzebub himself.</p>"; 
